{"data":{"mongodbDatabaseArticles":{"id":"5b93830087be056953db7e17","content":"<div><h1 name=\"9c9c\" id=\"9c9c\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf--leading graf--title\">The Ultimate List of Resources for Remote&#160;Workers</h1><p name=\"bbd9\" id=\"bbd9\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--h3\">Since the <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2013/11/13/lonely-planet-touristeye/\" class=\"markup--anchor markup--p-anchor\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">acquisition of my previous startup</a> 5 years ago, I&#8217;ve been working remotely and loving it. I&#8217;m now the founder of <a href=\"https://www.microverse.org/\" class=\"markup--anchor markup--p-anchor\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Microverse</a>, an online school for remote software developers where we teach our students how to take advantage of opportunities regardless of where they are.</p><p name=\"9520\" id=\"9520\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--p\"><strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">This guide is a living collection of resources that I often use or recommend to other people who want to become remote workers.</strong></p><p name=\"acf0\" id=\"acf0\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--p\">If you have anything that you want to add or update, please leave a comment.</p><h3 name=\"8ac7\" id=\"8ac7\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--p\">Conferences</h3><p class=\"aspectRatioPlaceholder-fill\"></p><img class=\"graf-image\" src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*UZ8QAj8s-pA65VRG46VPjg.jpeg\"><h3 name=\"da8c\" id=\"da8c\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--li\">Companies</h3><p name=\"1fae\" id=\"1fae\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--li\">Not enough? Check out this spreadsheet with more than other 600 companies hiring remotely:</p><h3 name=\"d0e4\" id=\"d0e4\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--mixtapeEmbed\">Communities</h3><h3 name=\"3c5f\" id=\"3c5f\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--li\">Co-living</h3><h3 name=\"202d\" id=\"202d\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--li\">Job boards</h3><h3 name=\"34c9\" id=\"34c9\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--li\">Newsletters</h3><h3 name=\"4c65\" id=\"4c65\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--li\">Books</h3><h3 name=\"19a4\" id=\"19a4\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--li\">Podcasts</h3><h3 name=\"9eaf\" id=\"9eaf\" class=\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--li\">Tools</h3><p name=\"4400\" id=\"4400\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--h3\"><strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">Communication</strong></p><p name=\"da28\" id=\"da28\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--li\"><strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">Video conferencing</strong></p><p name=\"7d5f\" id=\"7d5f\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--li\"><strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">Programming</strong></p><p name=\"0d5b\" id=\"0d5b\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--li\"><strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">Time tracking</strong></p><p name=\"5669\" id=\"5669\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--li\"><strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">Project management</strong></p><p name=\"4e48\" id=\"4e48\" class=\"graf graf--p graf-after--li\"><strong class=\"markup--strong markup--p-strong\">Timezone management</strong></p></div>","title":"The Ultimate List of Resources for Remote Workers â€“ Hacker Noon"}},"pageContext":{"id":"5b93830087be056953db7e17"}}